Madonna has revealed she was raped at knifepoint after arriving in New York as a 19-year-old dreaming of stardom.

The attack took place on a Manhattan rooftop, the 55-year-old star told Harper’s Bazaar magazine.

She said: ‘New York wasn’t everything I thought it would be. It did not welcome me with open arms.

