The star, who has four children – two of whom are adopted –  also reflects on her life after her divorce from British film director Guy Ritchie in 2008. 

‘Here I am, divorced and living in New York,’ she said. ‘I have been blessed with four amazing children.

'I try to teach them to think outside the box. To be daring.’

